Choose Your Equipment~
   Now you must choose your equipment.  Here you may buy any non magical item of
any type.  Simply type @Ybuy <vnum>@n to buy an item and @Ylist
<armor|weapon|other>@n to see what is available along with the vnum of the item
for buying, and its cost.  The amount of money you get is dependant on the class
you chose earlier in character generation.  Once you have purchased all of your
equipment, go north to prepare to enter the game.  
