Palanthas Stables~
   This area is used as a huge stables for all of the mounts that enter
Palanthas.  It even has an airie for griffons, wyverns, hypogriffs, giants
eagles, and even the odd dragon.  The area is absolutely huge.  A sign on the
wall reads @Ylist@n to see see what's available and @Ybuy@n to purchase a mount.
